**The anatomy of an image prompt:**

\

Prompts can be written in every way imaginable but the majority of prompts atleast have a description of the subject they want to render in their image. In addition, many users add aesthetic parameters that influence the visual properties of images. These parameters are terms which mention specific art styles, artists, art medium, aspect ration, color schemes and other abstract aesthetic qualities. Adding these terms to the prompt makes the AI model render the corresponding visual properties in an image.&nbsp;

